            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH7x2028-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:17:36.388+09:00">and such is what you are.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:27:06.473+09:00">The fire is burning our ruler's lower garments."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:15:10.305+09:00">Then he picked up the garment and the fire went out.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:15:35.201+09:00">The ruler was greatly incensed and said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:15:53.605+09:00">"You've known it for a long time/seen it a long time ago,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:16:14.699+09:00">why didn't you mention it earlier?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:16:25.001+09:00">The man in question said</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:20:26.067+09:00">One winter day when he was standing around a fireplace together with others</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:21:22.608+09:00">he noticed that the tailend somebody else's  lower garment had caught fire,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:21:30.454+09:00">and he went on to say:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:21:39.535+09:00">"There is a certain matter</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:21:53.225+09:00">which I have noticed quite some time ago,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:22:11.569+09:00">and I wanted to bring the matter up</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:22:48.944+09:00">but I was afraid His Lordship was hot-headed;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:23:01.545+09:00">but if I didn't bring it up</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:23:30.414+09:00">I was afraid Our Lordship would be too severely injured.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:23:49.51+09:00">Now then, would it be right to speak up on this?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:24:11.534+09:00">Or would it be right not to speak up on it?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:25:08.928+09:00">Someone else asked: "What matter?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:25:14.941+09:00">He said:</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
